name: firefox
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "77.0" %}

package:
  name: firefox
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/linux-x86_64/en-US/firefox-{{ version }}.tar.bz2  # [linux64]
  sha256: 7296e9e6b9a2f8d9aa5b9f42ce5672e8f29e9dd20924874a79d2ec6f57ffb33c  # [linux64]

  fn: firefox.pkg  # [osx]
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/mac/en-US/Firefox%20{{ version }}.pkg  # [osx]
  sha256: 82cf8b5c3c134e47fe0d47dacccb19e6af400ccc063b29c3f4b8226dfd76441c  # [osx]

  fn: firefox.msi  # [win]
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/win64/en-US/Firefox%20Setup%20{{ version }}.msi  # [win]
  sha256: 60d3da66d53a8882055c7ec1b38ef862a8022e23a18bcfba443e19122a5d581c  # [win]

build:
  number: 0
  binary_relocation:
    - bin/firefox

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}

test:
  requires:
    - selenium
    - geckodriver

about:
  home: https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/releases
  license: MPL-2.0
  license_family: MOZILLA
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Firefox web browser

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - birdsarah
    - ocefpaf
    - bollwyvl
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.7.3
